bib.title: 5th international symposium advances in Artificial Intelligence and applications
bib.author: Abonyi, Janos and Andersen, Hans Jorgen and Bartkowiak, Anna and Choras, Ryszard and Cios, Krzysztof and Cuzzocrea, Alfredo and De Stefano, Claudio and Da Deng, Jeremiah and Goczyla, Krzysztof and Goneid, Amr and others
bib.abstract: The AAIA'10 will bring researchers, developers, practitioners, and users to present their latest research, results, and ideas in all areas of artificial intelligence. We hope that theory and successful applications presented at the AAIA'10 will be of interest to researchers and practitioners who want to know about both theoretical advances and latest applied developments in Artificial Intelligence. As such AAIA'10 will provide a forum for the exchange of ideas between theoreticians and practitioners tp address the important issues.
